``policy labs are heavily based on design practice including design thinking and industrial design'' p100

Identified the REACT process in policy. This is two dimensional with one dimension being ontological and ranging from experienced reality to theoretical and the second describing the nature of involvment and ranging from inquiry to action: p100-101
- Redefinition the policy issue
