  comment          = {Present the ``interpretative policy entrepreneur'' [IPE] - add to Kingdon's PE the identification of activities establing meaning through framing mechanisms. Interview participants in the process of creating policy around a coastal protection/enhancement scheme in the Netherlands. The actors begin either happy with the current scheme (don't see any problem) or are keen to implement an innovative solution (they have a solution in mind).

